                    "displayName": "Client ID",
                    "description": "OAuth 2.0 Client ID. For partner-level (master) calls, use the Client ID issued by the SmartRecruiters Partner & API Team. For customer-level calls, use the Client ID returned by POST /apps-integrations/partner-api/integrations.",
